IR A115 case compatibility</h2><p class="SupportTab_explorer-content-paragraph__Uk7EM">The CORSAIR A115 is a big cooler for sure. So here's the info you need to make sure it will fit in your case.</p></div></a><a href="https://www.corsair.com/us/en/explorer/diy-builder/cases/reverse-motherboard-compatibility-with-corsair-cases/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" role="button" aria-label="Reverse Motherboard Compatibility with CORSAIR Cases" class="SupportTab_explorer-content-card__1DmIg flex-col flex w-full corsair-links"><img loading="lazy" src="https://d1q3zw97enxzq2.cloudfront.net/images/corsair_case_compatibility_with_r.width-500.format-webp.webp" alt="Reverse Motherboard Compatibility with CORSAIR Cases" class="object-cover bg-black" /><div class="SupportTab_explorer-cart-text__3q6Cw p-4 md:p-8 w-full h-full"><p class="font-semibold">BLOG</p><h2 class="leading-none mb-2">Reverse Motherboard Compatibility with CORSAIR Cases</h2><p class="SupportTab_explorer-content-paragraph__Uk7EM">We detail the CORSAIR cases compatible with MSI Project Zero, GIGABYTE Project Stealth, and ASUS BTF.</p></div></a><a href="https://www.corsair.com/us/en/explorer/diy-builder/cases/pc-cases-101-sizes-and-layouts/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" role="button" aria-label="PC Cases 101: Sizes and Layouts" class="SupportTab_explorer-content-card__1DmIg flex-col flex w-full corsair-links"><img loading="lazy" src="https://d1q3zw97enxzq2.cloudfront.net/images/pc_cases_101_sizes_and_layouts.width-500.format-webp.webp" alt="PC Cases 101: Sizes and Layouts" class="object-cover bg-black" /><div class="SupportTab_explorer-cart-text__3q6Cw p-4 md:p-8 w-full h-full"><p class="font-semibold">BLOG</p><h2 class="leading-none mb-2">PC Cases 101: Sizes and Layouts</h2><p class="SupportTab_explorer-content-paragraph__Uk7EM">Welcome to PC Cases 101: Class is in session. Today's lesson explains the different sizes and layouts of PC cases.</p></div></a><a href="https://www.corsair.com/us/en/explorer/diy-b